Package se.arkalix.security

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    X509ArrowheadName
    Describes an Arrowhead system, operator, cloud or company certificate.
    X509Certificates
    Helper functions for extracting information from x.509 certificates that is particularly relevant to the Arrowhead Framework.
    X509KeyStore
    Holds the x.509 certificates and private key required to manage an owned identity.
    X509KeyStore.Loader
    Helper class useful for creating X509KeyStore instances.
    X509Names
    Various utilities for working with LDAP Distinguished Names (DNs), which are, most significantly, used to identify the issuer and subject of x.509 certificates.
    X509TrustStore
    Holds x.509 certificates associated with trusted identities.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    X509NameException
    Represents the failure to parse an LDAP DN, potentially associated with some x.509 certificate.
